mmaryContaineruniface_104xzm1665702615183.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xzm1665702615183.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xzm1665702615183.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xzm1665702615183\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Controls the color value used as the default for inverse color objects.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xzm1665702615183__topic_d146426e1_d146427e1_d146428e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xzm1665702615183__p_d146429e1_d146430e1_d146431e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ColorInverse</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">IndexColor</var></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xzm1665702615183__section_dr1_dg4_yvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1025897e64\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xzm1665702615183__p_d146435e1_d146436e1_d146437e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">IndexColor</var>—Uniface index color</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Default Uniface Color Codes</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__1\">Color </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__2\">Foreground Color </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__3\">Background Color </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__1\">System default </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__2\">0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__3\">0 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__1\">Blue </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__2\">8 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__3\">1 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__1\">Green </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__2\">16 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__3\">2 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__1\">Cyan </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__2\">24 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__3\">3 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__1\">Red </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__2\">32 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__3\">4 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__1\">Purple </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__2\">40 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__3\">5 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__1\">Yellow </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__2\">48 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__3\">6 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__1\">White </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__2\">\n-\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__3\">7 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__1\">Black </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__2\">56 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17903e1_d17904e1_d17905e1__entry__3\">\n-\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xzm1665702615183__table_d17906e1_d17907e1_d17908e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">7 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yzj1665702614359.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yzj1665702614359.html\" title=\"The [upi] section of the initialization file determines the appearance or behavior of many Universal Presentation Interface (UPI) objects under Microsoft Windows.\">[upi]</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fya1665702645056.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uniface Index Colors</a><p>Uniface index colors are combinations of foreground an background colors that are identified by a color code, a number from 0 to 63.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533993\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533993\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ColorInverse Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 25, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Controls the color value used as the default for inverse color objects. ColorInverse = IndexColor Arguments IndexColor —Uniface index color Table 1. Default Uniface Color Codes Color Foreground Color Background Color System default 0 0 Blue 8 1 Green 16 2 Cyan 24 3 Red 32 4 Purple 40 5 Yellow 48 6 White - 7 Black 56 - Default value 7 File section [upi] Related Links Uniface Index Colors Uniface index colors are combinations of foreground an background colors that are identified by a color code, a number from 0 to 63. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}